{"tid":958263,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"溫兆倫喺義不容情演出算唔算精湛","createTime":"2018-12-27T16:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T07:29:05.000Z","uid":71166,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8eed2f2314d0a36e3b0ccc63eb731015c847a1b7","tid":958263,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢做得好好<br />\n由忠到貪再到奸都好有內心戲<br />\n又發揮得好好"},{"pid":"ef91c8e6e169b6f8caa7a0d5079ee03339b0d3d7","tid":958263,"uid":33099,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:07:29.000Z","msg":"幾時有忠過"},{"pid":"ad4acee9e0f7694b7b9a3ec5dbb73c7f1108886d","tid":958263,"uid":13885,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:09:18.000Z","msg":"做番自己 實好戲"},{"pid":"ccccb75f2e984ef08a44607c1420363e926234d4","tid":958263,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef91c8e6e169b6f8caa7a0d5079ee03339b0d3d7","tid":958263,"uid":33099,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:07:29.000Z","msg":"幾時有忠過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"初初唔算壞"},{"pid":"0704de1bb07d6d63d63a22f335a0f806efde1cdd","tid":958263,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad4acee9e0f7694b7b9a3ec5dbb73c7f1108886d","tid":958263,"uid":13885,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:09:18.000Z","msg":"做番自己 實好戲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T16:13:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">溫兆倫，近年轉戰內地賺人民幣，經常喺微博發表愛國偉論</span>，早前接受黨第一喉舌中央電視台節目《新春走基層》訪問，<span style=\"color: red;\">對住鏡頭講番當年自己對香港回歸嘅感受，話自己睇電視感動到喊，仲向國旗敬禮。</span><br />\n<br />\n喺央視接近兩分鐘嘅訪問片段中，溫兆倫憶述當年喺外國海關填寫入境表格，喺國藉一欄填寫「HongKong」，結果關員話唔啱，皆因香港只係一個地方。<span style=\"color: red;\">溫兆倫即刻交出一個痛苦到扭曲嘅表情：「我能寫中國嗎？我甚麼時候能寫中國？」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"